narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Take it if you are a Spike Lee fan.
I'd recommend this as a way to learn about an aspect of Black Cinema, considering the Whiteness of some other courses. But the class needs to be shorter.
An intense, rigorous discussion-based seminar that is like no other Yale experience. If you down to try something new and different, this is the class for you but be prepared for a wild ride.
